Jackbeat (A Simple Drum Machine)

Jackbeat is an audio sequencer running on Linux, Windows and OS X, for
musicians and sound artists: Drummachine interface with animations for easy and
playful editing Built for both composition and live setups with high
interactivity needs Extremely easy to use but yet powerful by connecting with
other applications and plugins using JACK and OSC Loads and saves .jab files,
Jackbeat's xml+tar open file format Supports native audio devices, PulseAudio
and JACK.
